 "contentEncoded": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://twitter.com/CRKendrick/status/1155487232\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://i42.tinypic.com/nqwe9d.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"491\" height=\"250\"></a></p>\n<p>Well, Nashville, we survived our first blizzard of 2009&#x2026; all twenty minutes of it. Since we&#x2019;re pretty sure this won&#x2019;t be happening again and we feel like we need to savor these moments, we&#x2019;ve decided to document the historic occasion with some of our favorite Tweets and Twitpics from you, the readers. One of the most endearing things about our city is that we&#x2019;re not really sure what to do when white stuff starts falling from the sky, so here&#x2019;s a small taste of the pandemonium.</p>\n<p><span id=\"more-1499\"></span></p>\n<p><strong>We laughed:</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://twitter.com/davedelaney/status/1155272157\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://i41.tinypic.com/2vb7m8k.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"516\" height=\"217\"></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://twitter.com/goggans/status/1155379663\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i44.tinypic.com/2gv3qer.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"514\" height=\"184\"></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">\n</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">\n</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>We cried:</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://twitter.com/Cabbage_Babble/status/1155383776\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://i42.tinypic.com/351isg4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"518\" height=\"212\"></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://twitter.com/haleybragg/status/1155442885\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i40.tinypic.com/10gmohk.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"515\" height=\"214\"></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://twitter.com/cpNashville/status/1155479201\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i40.tinypic.com/21nfnu1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"517\" height=\"211\"></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">\n</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">\n</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>We waxed poetic:</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://twitter.com/jamestealy/status/1155449535\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://i40.tinypic.com/28lqhhx.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"511\" height=\"226\"></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://twitter.com/geoffsmith/status/1155573761\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i44.tinypic.com/anbz2h.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"516\" height=\"186\"></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">\n</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">\n</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>We rolled our eyes:</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://twitter.com/rebekahm/status/1155461384\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://i39.tinypic.com/bgr347.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"521\" height=\"244\"></a></p>\n<p><strong>We snapped TwitPics:</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p>From @<a href=\"http://twitpic.com/188le\" target=\"_blank\">gavoweb</a>:</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://twitpic.com/188le\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i43.tinypic.com/pvzuh.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"405\" height=\"303\"></a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">From @<a href=\"http://twitpic.com/188r2\" target=\"_blank\">charleswvandyke</a>:</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://twitpic.com/188r2\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i41.tinypic.com/e9j52v.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"298\" height=\"370\"></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">\n</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>And finally, we waved goodbye</strong> to our blizzard because it all melted in an hour:</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://twitter.com/rhyminanstealin/status/1155624466\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://i43.tinypic.com/2dv02l4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"540\" height=\"247\"></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://twitter.com/JustinFratt/status/1155615729\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i44.tinypic.com/34oegw9.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"535\" height=\"190\"></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://twitter.com/laura_jeanette/status/1155458934\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://i44.tinypic.com/mijl.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"540\" height=\"219\"></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n   \t\t\t</p>"
